  "texts": [
    "We then computed a p value for the difference between the test embedding and the nearest training embedding based on this null distribution.",
    "This procedure was repeated to produce a p value for each lag and we corrected for multiple tests using FDR.",
    "To compare the difference between classifier performance using IFG embedding or precentral embedding for each lag, we used a paired sample t-test.",
    "We compared the AUC of each word classified with the IFG or precentral embedding for each lag.",
    "We used Bonferroni correction to account for the multiple comparisons."
